def δ (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : x > 0 then
    Nat.find (Exists.intro (Nat.gcdOdd x) (⟨Nat.gcdOdd_div x h, Nat.gcdOdd_least x h⟩))
  else 1

def delta (x : ℕ) : ℕ :=
  if h : x > 0 then
    Nat.find_greatest (fun d => d % 2 = 1 ∧ d ∣ x) (x / 2 + 1)
  else 0
